I’m a **Salesforce Marketing Cloud (SFMC) Senior Executive** with 3.9 years of experience delivering personalized, data-driven marketing journeys.  
I specialize in **automation, AI personalization, CRM integration, A/B testing, and SQL segmentation** for multi-channel campaigns (Email, SMS, WhatsApp, Push).  
